RESULT: The control relay and both Control Output Cables (+) and (−) show nominal low resistance/continuity values. With the output unloaded and referenced to the input − node, the Control Output Cable (+) measures 0.3592 V DC. No POLARITY INVERSION DETECTED in the measured cabling.
